    • Field Detail

      • label

        public java.lang.String label
        The legend entry text. A `null` label will start a group.

      • form

        public Legend.LegendForm form
        The form to draw for this entry. `NONE` will avoid drawing a form, and any related space. `EMPTY` will avoid drawing a form, but keep its space. `DEFAULT` will use the Legend's default.

      • formSize

        public float formSize
        Form size will be considered except for when .None is used Set as NaN to use the legend's default

      • formLineWidth

        public float formLineWidth
        Line width used for shapes that consist of lines. Set as NaN to use the legend's default

      • formLineDashEffect

        public android.graphics.DashPathEffect formLineDashEffect
        Line dash path effect used for shapes that consist of lines. Set to null to use the legend's default

      • formColor

        public int formColor
        The color for drawing the form

        Parameters:
        label - The legend entry text. A `null` label will start a group.
        form - The form to draw for this entry.
        formSize - Set to NaN to use the legend's default.
        formLineWidth - Set to NaN to use the legend's default.
        formLineDashEffect - Set to nil to use the legend's default.
        formColor - The color for drawing the form.
